â”‚     â”‚     âœ•      â”‚ â† Use center punch                  â”‚
â”‚     â”‚            â”‚                                     â”‚
â”‚     â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜                                     â”‚
â”‚                                                        â”‚
â”‚  2. Start with pilot hole (3mm):                       â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ Use low drill speed                              â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ Apply gentle pressure                            â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ For acrylic: place tape over area (prevents cracks)â”‚
â”‚                                                        â”‚
