â”‚     â€¢ Use step drill bit (best for clean holes)        â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ OR use progressively larger drill bits           â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ Go slow, let tool do the work                    â”‚
â”‚                                                        â”‚
â”‚  4. Deburr edges:                                      â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ Use deburring tool or sandpaper                  â”‚
â”‚     â€¢ Smooth both sides of hole                        â”‚
â”‚                                                        â”‚
