## ğŸ“¦ FINAL WIRING CHECKLIST
```
JOYSTICKS:
â˜ Left VCC â†’ 3V3
â˜ Left GND â†’ GND
â˜ Left VRx â†’ A0
â˜ Left VRy â†’ A1
â˜ Left SW â†’ D16 (optional)

â˜ Right VCC â†’ 3V3 (share with Left)
â˜ Right GND â†’ GND (share with Left)
â˜ Right VRx â†’ A2
â˜ Right VRy â†’ A3
â˜ Right SW â†’ D17 (optional)

BUTTONS (16 total):
â˜ A â†’ D5 + GND
â˜ B â†’ D6 + GND
â˜ X â†’ D9 + GND
â˜ Y â†’ D10 + GND
â˜ Up â†’ D11 + GND
â˜ Down â†’ D12 + GND
â˜ Left â†’ D13 + GND
â˜ Right â†’ D4 + GND
â˜ L1 â†’ D24 + GND
â˜ L2 â†’ D25 + GND
â˜ R1 â†’ D2 + GND
â˜ R2 â†’ D3 + GND
â˜ Start â†’ D0 + GND
â˜ Select â†’ D1 + GND
â˜ L3 â†’ D16 + GND
â˜ R3 â†’ D17 + GND

POWER:
â˜ USB-C to RPi 5
â˜ All GNDs common
```

